metadata.name: Spootato | Fantastic Creatures
metadata.description:
''Spootato is a broken soul. All he ever wanted was to make people happy. What went wrong? That's a very long story...''

**strenghts**
He's literally food.

**weaknesses**
Always hungry, usually in a bad mood, doesn't have many friends.

**Rarity:** Common
**Beast Rank:** 1 out of 9



*''Realistified: Fantastic Creatures'' is a an NFT colletion containing trading cards of the Creatures responsible for making Benny's career what it is today. The notorious YouTube Photoshop series ''Realistified'' is all about bringing Drawings to life. These beasts are from different episodes of season one and are now available as fantasy trading cards.*

*Just like other trading cards they're all unique and have their own strengths, weaknesses and character. Some creatures are common, others are super rare. For example the Phoenix we all know and love is a legendary card in this collection. This has been a project in the works for quite some time. Season two is being worked on as we speak.*
